item.title: Help me!
item.dc:creator: @watch_n_lern watch n lern
item.description:
@watch_n_lern wrote:

websites say it is offline if you are using hamachi to connect to your server as it does not allow pings. Also are you sure your client isnt connecting to the ip “127.0.0.1”? search for “ip” in the client.java notepad on the client side. and change to your no-ip then you need to compile it.
